text: Reza Yazdani (, born October 16, 1973) is an Iranian singer, musician, composer, and actor. He is an Iranian Pop rock musician and has released eight albums and numerous single songs till now. He has performed live concerts since the release of his third album, Hiss, mainly in Milad Tower Concert Hall. ==References== * Category:Iranian singers Category:Actors from Tehran Category:Living people Category:1973 births
